Pre-Game Insights: West Indies qualified for the Super 8 with a perfect points tally.
England's road to the knockouts was not that pretty, but they still managed to qualify as the second-placed team from Group B.
Both West Indies and England have met many times for competitive series across different formats.
Miscellaneous Highlights: West Indies thrashed Afghanistan by 104 runs in their recent match.
England decimated Oman in their Group B match, bowling them out for just 47 and then chasing down the target with 101 balls and 8 wickets to spare.
